-- ON_ERROR_STOP / RAISE EXCEPTION combination.
--
-- Companion documents:
--   /opt/wdws/rcw_research/rcw_source_findings.md
--   /opt/wdws/rcw_research/cross_jurisdiction_design.md
--   /opt/wdws/rcw_research/litigation_priority_addendum.md
