--   psql -h 127.0.0.1 -U wdws -d wdws -f /opt/wdws/rcw_research/schema_apply.sql
--
-- Expected behavior:
--   1. Pre-flight guards print "PASS" NOTICE or RAISE EXCEPTION
--   2. §1 schema + §2 indexes + §3 tag inserts execute
--   3. §LEGACY-MIGRATION re-points 5 join rows + deletes 2 legacy tag rows
--   4. §4 USC retroactive tagging adds 11,678 join rows
--   5. Post-apply guards print "PASS" NOTICE or RAISE EXCEPTION
--   6. COMMIT succeeds OR full ROLLBACK on any failure
--   7. Post-commit verification SELECTs print to stdout
--
-- Capture the entire psql output (stdout + stderr) and paste back to the
-- agent for parsing and Phase 2 authorization decision.
