-- Estimated wall time: under 30 seconds total. The 11,678-row USC retro-tag
-- INSERT is the largest operation; everything else is trivial.
--
-- If the script raises an EXCEPTION, the transaction rolls back automatically.
-- Database is unchanged. Report the exception text and any preceding NOTICE
-- messages back to the agent.
